                </div>
                <p>The Yezdi Adventure comes with a purposeful stance — tall, rugged, and ready for dirt. It gets:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>High-mounted mudguard</li>
                    <li>Integrated crash guard</li>
                    <li>Functional pannier mounts</li>
                    <li>Simple yet muscular design language</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="subheading"><a class="for-link" asp-controller="RoyalEnfield" asp-action="REHimalyan">Himalayan 450</a></h3>
